FBIS4-26733 "drchi123_o_94005" FBIS-CHI-94-123 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 REGIONAL AFFAIRS$ East Region Shanghai Reports Executions of Three People Shanghai Reports Executions of Three People OW2506165994 Shanghai People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 21 Jun 94 OW2506165994 Shanghai People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [From the "990 Morning News" program] [Text] Yesterday, the municipal intermediate court harshly punished three persons who had committed serious violent crimes of murder and robbery. In accordance with the municipal high court's death-sentence order, murderer (Yu Yucai) was dragged to the execution ground for execution. The municipal intermediate court also handed down death sentences on (Zhang Qijiang) and (Lu Huaqing), who, armed with knives, robbed their victims.
